  <summary>6/10/1997--Introduced.
Local Free Access Act - Amends provisions regarding Federal payments in lieu of taxes to exempt persons residing within the boundaries of local governments that receive such payments from National Forest System recreational user fees unless sufficient funds are appropriated in a fiscal year to provide full payments to eligible local governments.</summary>
